Can't the effect of this be accomplished in a completely portable fashion
entirely in user space?
	mkdir /interpreters
	cd /interpreters
	chmod 755 .
	for i in perl awk bash csh sed; do
		ln -s `type -path $i` $i
	done
Scripts would then use
	#!/interpreters/perl
to run perl, etc.
--Tim Smith
